figured out his General Relativity

Einstein had figured out that gravity
could actually warp the fabric of space and time
  -- brilliantly fascinating idea proven with some brilliant maths --

but there was a problem because the maths also showed something
that couldn't possibly be
it appeared that the warping of space and time
would violate the maths most fundamental laws --
